{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fc31c0d9c2","title":"给诗刊的一封信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8ec84f6cd2","index":0,"year":1957,"month":1,"day":12,"articleId":"fc31c0d9c2"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1949.10-1957.12）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"861e0244f9","type":"paragraph","text":"给舒刊的一封信","index":0,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"fc31c0d9c2"},{"id":"03ef8a25c1","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九五七年一月十二日）XX同志和各位同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"fc31c0d9c2"},{"id":"6e480f0d36","type":"paragraph","text":"慧书早已收到，退复为款！遵将记得起来的旧体诗词，连同你们寄来的八首，一共十八首，抄寄如另纸，请加审处。","index":2,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"fc31c0d9c2"},{"id":"8ac1eed2de","type":"paragraph","text":"这些东西，我历来不愿意正式发表，因为是旧体，怕种流传，遗误责年；再则诗珠不多，没有什么特色。既然你们以为可以刊载，又可为已经传抄的几首改正错字，那么，就照你们的意见办吧。","index":3,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"fc31c0d9c2"},{"id":"71973012fb","type":"paragraph","text":"诗刊出版，很好，就它成长发展。诗当然应以新诗为主体，旧诗可以写一些，但是不宜在青年中提倡，因为这种体裁束续思想，又不易学。这些话仅供你们参考。","index":4,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"fc31c0d9c2"},{"id":"b7c16cc399","type":"paragraph","text":"同志的敬冠！","index":5,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"fc31c0d9c2"},{"id":"8173067c52","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":6,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"fc31c0d9c2"},{"id":"ae8bb864b6","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五七年一月十二日在省市委书记会静上的插汇集","index":7,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"fc31c0d9c2"},{"id":"db8d29c539","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九五七年一月）","index":8,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"fc31c0d9c2"},{"id":"744b16788d","type":"paragraph","text":"、思想斗争间题","index":9,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"fc31c0d9c2"},{"id":"0a54fcb423","type":"paragraph","text":"去年下牛年以来，有一股右倾机会主义的风，在地面之上，云层之下流动。党内外有一股反社会主义的逆流。","index":10,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"fc31c0d9c2"},{"id":"abca86d3c1","type":"paragraph","text":"对社会上的歪风，一定要打下去。打的办法要有说服力，不是简单骂几句。如果简单粗暴，则至风越刮越大。","index":11,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"fc31c0d9c2"},{"id":"980c705d45","type":"paragraph","text":"今年五月人代会，七月政协会，怪议论一定会多。一个是法制，一个是农民苦，一个是没肉吃。总的是社会主义有没有优越性。要准备打这两仗，在座的代表要出马参战，每人准备一篇，要有分析。","index":12,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"fc31c0d9c2"},{"id":"dc0de24052","type":"paragraph","text":"同小资产阶级特别是富裕中农思想作斗争，要反复斗争多少年，富裕中农的影响很大，特别厉害，应当注意。","index":13,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"fc31c0d9c2"},{"id":"9dec87d053","type":"paragraph","text":"光搞业务工作，不搞思想工作，就会闹乱子。","index":14,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"fc31c0d9c2"},{"id":"fb13935e60","type":"paragraph","text":"每个省要有一、二个马克思，一、二个鲁迅。你们应该写文章，六十岁以下的都应该写。","index":15,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"fc31c0d9c2"}],"page":{"id":"2aa148d600","publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"fc31c0d9c2","start":134,"end":134}}}},"__N_SSG":true}